rows.label: qev300031_MSG0002
rows.name:
I tell you, between Skell maintenance and the other
heavy machinery, we really chew through the stuff.
I could use about 1,800 units this time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300031_SEL0021
rows.name: Hold on to your miranium for now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300031_MSG0004
rows.name: Thanks a bunch. See you again soon, I hope?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300031_MSG0005
rows.name: No dice? Well, give a shout if you change your mind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300031_MSG0006
rows.name:
Huh. Don't think you've quite got 1,800 units there.
I'd prefer to get it all at once if you don't mind,
so whenever you get it in, just lemme know.[ST:wait ]
